        auto-filter architecture. Failure modes differ; parts supply differs; service protocols differ. Both
        systems work well when maintained; both degrade when maintenance is skipped.
      </p>
      <p>
        <b>Market position.</b> Pitco has the #1 US market share in commercial fryers, broadest installed base,
        strongest multi-vendor parts availability, most extensive service network nationwide. Frymaster has the
        McDonald's OEM relationship spanning 50+ years (H17 legacy and current FilterQuick generations), which
        makes Frymaster ubiquitous across McDonald's franchise operations and adjacent QSR ecosystems.
      </p>
      <p>
        <b>Build and controls.</b> Roughly comparable premium-tier engineering. Pitco leans on Bow NH manufacturing
